    {
      "para_id": "Q001959.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Lipit-Eštar , the humble shepherd of Nibru , the true farmer of Urim , ceaseless provider of Eridug , the en priest suitable for Unug , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the favourite of Inana , the king who established justice in Sumer and Akkad ."
    }
  ],
